  "text": "Thank you. When you spoke in the last session of \"energizing shocks\" coming from the top of the pyramid, did you mean that these came at intervals rather than steadily? I am Ra. These energizing shocks come at discrete intervals but come very, very close together in a properly functioning pyramid shape. In one whose dimensions have gone awry the energy will not be released with regularity or in quanta, as you may perhaps better understand our meaning.",
